      <title>汽车芯片市场持续低迷，意法半导体营收下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stmicro-s-revenue-drops-as-slump-in-automotive-chips-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意法半导体 (STMicroelectronics NV) 公布第二季度销售额下滑，原因是库存过剩和对汽车制造商的销售额下降抑制了需求。]]></description>
